When `orgId` IS present (existing "connect to org" flow from sources page), the callback continues to the existing reactivation detection + `gatewayInstallations` upsert. **No changes to this path.** The `providerOrgId` column stays NULL for connections made through the existing flow; the follow-up backfill PR will populate these values via the validate flow.

